<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-honour-of-sb-in-sbs-honour">in honour of sb / in sb's honour</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>为向某人表示敬意；为纪念某人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We celebrate Mother's Day in honour of our mothers.
我们庆祝母亲节是为了向母亲表示敬意。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A ceremony was held in those soldiers' honour.
人们举行了一个仪式来纪念那些战士。</p></div></div>